DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that a new user can be created and the response contains the correct user data.
NAME: Create New User

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies unsuccessful registration with missing password.
NAME: Unsuccessful Registration Test

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies the response when attempting to retrieve a user that does not exist.
NAME: Single User Not Found

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies successful registration with valid email and password.
NAME: Successful Registration Test

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that the system can handle a delayed response correctly.
NAME: Handle Delayed Response

DESCRIPTION: Tests a successful login attempt and checks for the presence and validity of the token.
NAME: Successful Login Test

DESCRIPTION: This test retrieves details of a single user by ID and verifies the response structure
NAME: Get Single User Details

DESCRIPTION: Tests an unsuccessful login attempt due to missing password and verifies error messages.
NAME: Unsuccessful Login Test

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that a partial update to an existing user is successful and the response contains the updated data.
NAME: Partial Update Existing User

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that an existing user can be updated and the response contains the updated user data.
NAME: Update Existing User

DESCRIPTION: This test retrieves a list of users from page 2 and verifies the response structure and content.
NAME: Get List of Users

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that an existing user can be deleted successfully and that a subsequent request to retrieve the user returns a 404 status code.
NAME: Delete Existing User
